DracoPKG

http://www.dracolinux.org - http://github.com/dracolinux

Copyright (c) 2014 Ole Andre Rodlie <olear@dracolinux.org>. All rights reserved.

ABOUT

DracoPKG is a package management suite for DracoLinux and compatible.

INSTALL

qmake && make install

Example:

qmake PREFIX=/usr LIBSUFFIX=64 && make INSTALL_ROOT=/tmp install

